#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:104
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "With the third page (the right screen shot) you define the dictionary for "
#| "a word completion. &kmouth; will parse the &kde; documentation of the "
#| "chosen language in order to detect the frequentness of individual words. "
#| "Optionally you can compare the word list to an OpenOffice.org dictionary "
#| "in order to only add correctly spelled words to the word completion."
msgid ""
"With the third page you define the dictionary for a word completion. "
"&kmouth; will parse the &kde; documentation of the chosen language in order "
"to detect the regularity of individual words. Optionally you can compare the "
"word list to an OpenOffice.org dictionary in order to only add correctly "
"spelled words to the word completion."
msgstr ""
"Na stronie trzeciej (prawa strona ekranu) możesz zdefiniować słownik "
